{"tid":1349322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰今日繼續提供義載 睇下有冇巴打需要","createTime":"2019-07-22T10:02:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T17:06:50.000Z","uid":107060,"like":122,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"58297ff586f03b590eac85c9f8cfdfab77093180","tid":1349322,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:02:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QEfRq3H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQEfRq3H.jpg&h=5ceada6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"734e229189ece2f714c9ef11549bab5d3406110e","tid":1349322,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:09:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac24e095a0784b7c03fce768b8de22921d5f099","tid":1349322,"uid":107060,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:09:56.000Z","msg":"據悉，博愛醫院及屯門醫院有大量醫護學生進行實習，而護士學校及醫院並沒有安排早放，有學生需要當值至晚上9點至10點許才下班。<br />\n<br />\n大家可以把我們的安全接送車隊的聯絡發給他們，或不能提早下班的朋友，我們盡力提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n//（15:45）<br />\n<br />\n今日不斷收到各方消息及相片，指屯門、元朗、天水圍一帶均可能出現街頭廝殺或黑幫隨機襲擊途人的情況。<br />\n<br />\n我們的安全車隊，如大家有需要，請隨時與 6371 2807（鄧文傑）聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n敬請注意，各種緊急狀況亦有可能出現，等候安排時請先確保自己安全。//"},{"pid":"c9075f5f15f468ba759ba861b2b6f6333e2e8c97","tid":1349322,"uid":273719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:10:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a28c1258b63f06d26fc55a8effa4f592d58d9336","tid":1349322,"uid":62523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:10:32.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"2b24ca993919b56acafb6a7ca6fb53280368a4b1","tid":1349322,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:13:25.000Z","msg":"博愛醫院返工人士注意"},{"pid":"3e6445d78b85b903f4936cddad6d345db4e221e2","tid":1349322,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T10:19:45.000Z","msg":"博愛醫院返工人士注意"},{"pid":"86154c40f8a18665a9e125e5e73e64c3c016ac91","tid